The next factor, the fifth one, the fifth factor is the state tax and subsidies.

01:15:27.000 --> 01:15:31.000
How does it affect the offer?

01:15:32.000 --> 01:15:34.000
Well, taxes are actually different.

01:15:35.000 --> 01:15:39.000
Let's take those taxes that increase the costs of the producers.

01:15:40.000 --> 01:15:42.000
So, the taxes are the same costs.

01:15:43.000 --> 01:15:49.000
When we introduce a tax, the costs of the producers increase by a large amount.

01:15:50.000 --> 01:15:52.000
The tax and the supply curve go up.

