The supply curve decreases.

01:15:55.000 --> 01:15:56.000
What is a subsidy?

01:15:57.000 --> 01:16:00.000
A subsidy is a tax, on the contrary.

01:16:01.000 --> 01:16:03.000
When the state doesn't take money, it gives it to the producers.

01:16:04.000 --> 01:16:06.000
Taking into account the subsidies, the costs decrease.

01:16:07.000 --> 01:16:11.000
And the supply curve goes down to the amount of subsidies.

01:16:12.000 --> 01:16:15.000
The purpose and the natural conditions are not complicated.

