Most likely, they will hold on to the goods.

01:16:52.000 --> 01:16:54.000
They won't rush to sell it.

01:16:55.000 --> 01:16:56.000
And what will happen?

01:16:57.000 --> 01:17:03.000
The supply will decrease and the curve will go up.

