it is possible to achieve

01:54:46.000 --> 01:54:48.000
that labor and capital are used

01:54:49.000 --> 01:54:51.000
in the most rational way.

01:54:55.000 --> 01:54:59.000
What do these parameters mean?

01:55:00.000 --> 01:55:03.000
Let's start with parameter A.

01:55:04.000 --> 01:55:05.000
Look, please.

01:55:06.000 --> 01:55:10.000
Imagine that the quantities of capital and labor are given,

01:55:13.000 --> 01:55:15.000
and parameter A changes.

01:55:16.000 --> 01:55:17.000
What does this mean?

01:55:18.000 --> 01:55:22.000
That with the same quantities of capital and labor,

01:55:23.000 --> 01:55:26.000
we can get a larger volume of output.

01:55:27.000 --> 01:55:30.000
So parameter A reflects the influence

01:55:31.000 --> 01:55:34.000
of technical progress on production function.

