02:21:20.000 --> 02:21:23.000
And what are your unobvious expenses for the arcade?

02:21:27.000 --> 02:21:33.000
I assume that you don't have a free place in the cafe.

02:21:34.000 --> 02:21:37.000
Therefore, if you install an arcade in this corner,

