Accordingly, the lost profit from the table

02:21:47.000 --> 02:21:49.000
will be included in the unobvious expenses for the arcade.

02:21:50.000 --> 02:21:52.000
You can't ignore the unobvious expenses.

02:21:53.000 --> 02:21:54.000
Otherwise, you can't understand

02:21:55.000 --> 02:21:57.000
how profitable or unprofitable it is for you to install an arcade.

